{
  "stem": "11882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was-- you couldn't be that stupid, even Hitler, to want to start another war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so I didn't register that we were coming right up close to a war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Not like my mentor, Robert Kempner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He already knew long before that a war was coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He always said, Hitler means war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When he came in, it means war for the German people and the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But at any rate, the Brazilian deal didn't materialize fast enough, and Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Sachs didn't feel any great-- Martin Sachs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "S-A-C-H-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "God rest his soul.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But anyway, Martin Sachs didn't work fast enough and didn't feel too hurried.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He led a somewhat isolated life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was very pathetic, personally, at the table, when he would say, Fraulein-- I don't remember her name-- Fraulein Miller spoke to me today on the street.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that was a former close employee of his, I don't know, secretary or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she had had the courage to speak to him on the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was really worth telling to Anna-- Fraulein Annie, the governess, and his daughter, and me, and usually a guest of the family, someone there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was very pathetic, you know, that meant so much to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And Fraulein Annie told me, the governess, I have a real problem.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You know, he loves Annamarie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That was the apple of his eye, his Annamarie, his little 14-year-old daughter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She doesn't like to have him take a walk with her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She doesn't want to be seen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He was a noted man in the town, the richest man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Biggest taxpayer in Herschberg, he told me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And lied-- probably that was his misfortune, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But he didn't realize that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He thought that was a contribution.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He had done his best for the politicians.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
